<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title></title>
</head>
<body>
     <div class="flex flex-col min-h-screen md:flex-row outline-dashed container mx-auto w-[50vw] md:min-h-0 md:h-[70vh]  space-x-10  mt-10">

        <!-- movie picture container -->
        <div class="container outline-dashed mx-auto md:mx-0 w-[30vw] h-full ">
          <img src="../images/Films/blade-runner.jpeg" class="object-cover  h-full"  alt="movie picture">
        </div>
        <!-- movie detail -->
        <div class="container outline-dashed flex flex-col h-full  w-[40vw] justify-start items-start space-y-6 py-8">
          <!-- movie title -->
          <h1 class="font-arvo text-blueOne font-bold text-4xl">
            Blade Runner
          </h1>

          <!-- movie score button-->
          <button class="w-28 h-12 bg-blueOne p-1 space-x-2 flex items-center justify-center group hover:scale-95 duration-200 ease-out">
            <div class="mb-0.5">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="25" height="25" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path fill="white" d="M20 8h-5.612l1.123-3.367c.202-.608.1-1.282-.275-1.802S14.253 2 13.612 2H12c-.297 0-.578.132-.769.36L6.531 8H4c-1.103 0-2 .897-2 2v9c0 1.103.897 2 2 2h13.307a2.01 2.01 0 0 0 1.873-1.298l2.757-7.351A1 1 0 0 0 22 12v-2c0-1.103-.897-2-2-2M4 10h2v9H4zm16 1.819L17.307 19H8V9.362L12.468 4h1.146l-1.562 4.683A.998.998 0 0 0 13 10h7z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <p class="font-arvo text-white text-xl font-bold">
              Noter
            </p>
          </button>

          <!-- movie info -->
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 text-sm">

            <div class="flex items-center space-x-1">
              <div class="mb-1 flex items-center">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="text-blueOne" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path fill="currentColor" fill-rule="evenodd" d="M11.277 4.781A4 4 0 0 1 14.606 3h.213a2 2 0 0 1 1.973 2.329L16.18 9h2.38a3 3 0 0 1 2.942 3.588l-1.2 6A3 3 0 0 1 17.36 21H6a3 3 0 0 1-3-3v-8a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3.93a1 1 0 0 0 .832-.445zM7 11H5v7a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h1z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
              </div>
              <p class="text-blueOne font-arvo font-bold">248</p>
            </div>

            <p class="font-arvo text-blueOne font-bold">1h31</p>
            <p class="font-arvo text-blueOne font-bold">Science-fiction</p>

          </div>

          <div class="container text-nowrap flex flex-col text-xs">
            <p class="font-arvo text-blueOne font-bold">Sortie : 01 mai 2024</p>
            <p class="font-arvo text-blueOne font-bold">Avec Ryan Gosling, Harrison Ford, de Denis Villeneuve </p>
          </div>

          <div class="container">
            <p class="font-arvo text-blueOne w-[70%]">
              En 2049, la société est fragilisée par les nombreuses tensions entre les humains et leurs esclaves créés par bio-ingénierie. L'officier K est un blade runner: il fait partie d'une force...
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- movie reservation button -->
          <button class="w-44 h-12 bg-goldOne p-1 space-x-2 flex items-center justify-center group hover:scale-95 duration-200 ease-out">
            <p class="font-arvo text-white text-xl font-bold">
              Réserver
            </p>
          </button>

        </div>

      </div>
</body>
</html>